snippet.title: Tacti-Cat SAGE '23 Final trailer
snippet.description:
SAGE '23 is finally here and with it comes the newest build of Tacti-Cat, I cannot overstate how happy I am to have my little game in SAGE.

This time I made everything (except the sage intro) that went into the trailer.

The Tacti-Cat 0.09 SAGE '23 Demo is available to download RIGHT NOW: https://null3d.itch.io/tacti-cat
https://null3d.itch.io/tacti-cat

DOWNLOAD IT.

NOW.
